@startuml UC11_Sequence
title UC11: 成绩统计分析 - 顺序图

actor "教师" as Teacher
boundary "教师成绩分析页面" as StatsPage
control "成绩控制类" as GradeCtrl
entity "Grade" as Grade

Teacher -> StatsPage : 选择课程查看统计
StatsPage -> GradeCtrl : getGradeStats(courseId)
GradeCtrl -> Grade : findByCourse(courseId)
Grade --> GradeCtrl : gradeList
GradeCtrl -> GradeCtrl : generateReport(gradeList)
GradeCtrl --> StatsPage : 返回分布及格率等图表数据
StatsPage -> Teacher : 展示分析图表
@enduml
